statements.sql: select `workspaces`.*, `user_workspaces`.`permission` from `workspaces` inner join `user_workspaces` on `workspaces`.`id` = `user_workspaces`.`workspace_id` where `workspaces`.`id` = 1 and `user_id` = 2 limit 1

select `tasks`.*, `stages`.`name` as `stage`, `stages`.`complete` from `tasks` inner join `user_projects` on `tasks`.`project_id` = `user_projects`.`project_id` inner join `projects` on `projects`.`id` = `user_projects`.`project_id` inner join `stages` on `stages`.`id` = `tasks`.`status` where `user_id` = 2 and `projects`.`workspace` = 1 order by `due_date` asc
